Always use Tailwind CSS for styling, never inline styles
All components go in /components folder
All pages use the App Router in /app folder
Use TypeScript throughout
Use only brand colours from the asset SVGs: brand-purple (#9739b0), brand-yellow (#f3d02a), brand-white (#FFFFFF); optional brand-purple-light (#be76ef) from Primary Logo Light Purple.svg for accents
Use brand fonts loaded from the user's Specialist Movers email signature folder (Inter + Termina) via next/font/local
Mobile first — always style mobile then desktop
Keep components small and reusable
Never use stock photos — use clearly labelled placeholder divs styled with purple/yellow/white only
Quote form component lives at components/QuoteForm.tsx and is reused across all pages
